14:44.551 --> 14:46.827
- That's a neat trick.

14:46.896 --> 14:49.379
What trick?

14:49.448 --> 14:52.379
-  Are you
seeing tricky things, Liza?

14:55.862 --> 14:57.413
- Nev--never mind me.

14:57.482 --> 15:00.413
I'm just--I'm just
feeling a little funny.

15:00.482 --> 15:03.655
Oh, that's right.

15:03.724 --> 15:05.620
You're a drug super-taster.

15:05.689 --> 15:07.068
- I am?

15:07.137 --> 15:10.517
- Yeah! Remember
the lollipot in Jersey?

15:10.586 --> 15:12.310
What's a lollipot?

15:12.379 --> 15:14.448
-  It's
a weird story from the past.

15:14.517 --> 15:16.965
- You know, I'm gonna--
I'm gonna go see the nurse.

15:17.034 --> 15:18.172
I'll go with you.

15:18.241 --> 15:19.275
I'll go with you.

15:19.344 --> 15:20.448
- We'll go with you.

15:20.517 --> 15:21.931
- No.

15:22.000 --> 15:24.068
No.

15:24.137 --> 15:25.793
Don't...just...

15:25.862 --> 15:28.517
stay.

15:28.586 --> 15:31.172
Just...you stay.

15:31.241 --> 15:34.655
Okay...

15:45.586 --> 15:47.275
- Oh. Okay.

15:48.862 --> 15:51.137
Hi.
- Hi.

15:51.206 --> 15:53.172
- I'm feeling a little weird.

15:53.241 --> 15:55.137
Are you Nurse Maureen?

15:56.000 --> 15:57.896
Travis Jason
said to come find you

15:57.965 --> 16:00.068
if I was having any issues,

16:00.137 --> 16:02.965
and I am definitely
having some issues.

16:03.034 --> 16:05.551
- This is a safe space.

16:05.620 --> 16:07.551
- Help!

16:07.620 --> 16:09.172
Oh! Wait.

16:09.241 --> 16:11.896
Wait--

16:11.965 --> 16:14.517
Hey! You!

16:14.586 --> 16:15.862
Hey, you! Help!

16:15.931 --> 16:18.448
Oh!

16:18.517 --> 16:20.931
Hi! Call 911!

16:24.793 --> 16:27.517
Really?

16:27.586 --> 16:29.517
Oh, God!

16:29.586 --> 16:32.413
Help!

16:39.275 --> 16:40.689
Okay.

16:47.965 --> 16:49.172
Aah!

16:49.241 --> 16:51.689
Oh.
Whew.

16:52.827 --> 16:54.310
I'm done.
Are you?

16:54.379 --> 16:56.034
Oh, God.

16:56.103 --> 16:58.137
- Is the universe trying
to tell me something

16:58.206 --> 16:59.965
by putting Josh here
just when Charles and I

17:00.034 --> 17:02.103
are having this roadblock?

17:02.172 --> 17:05.241
I imagined Josh
in my room last night.

17:05.310 --> 17:08.344
I mean, it wasn't even real,
but I feel guilty

17:08.413 --> 17:10.551
for my own thoughts.
- Been there.

17:10.620 --> 17:13.793
- Oh, Josh is so beautiful.

17:13.862 --> 17:16.000
Every time I look at him,

17:16.068 --> 17:17.551
I have flashes of our sex.

17:17.620 --> 17:19.896
